{
  "info": {
    "name": "Cleanup Operations Tests - Phase 13",
    "description": "Supplemental DELETE operations for resources that currently lack cleanup tests.\n\nThis collection resolves the CRUD incompleteness gap identified in the analysis:\n- Companies: CREATE exists, DELETE missing\n- Licenses: CREATE exists, DELETE missing\n- SingleLink Templates: CREATE exists, DELETE missing\n- Users: CREATE exists, DELETE missing\n\nBase URLs:\n- SignerAPI: {{baseUrl}} = https://devtest.comda.co.il/api/v3/\n- ManagementAPI: {{managementBaseUrl}} = https://devtest.comda.co.il/managementapi/v3/\n\n**Purpose:**\nPrevents test data accumulation by providing cleanup operations for all created resources.\nEach DELETE test includes proper error handling for nonexistent resources (404 or 204 idempotent).\n\n**Prerequisites:**\nThese tests assume that resource IDs have been captured in collection variables:\n- testCompanyId (from Phase 10 Company creation)\n- testLicenseKey (from Phase 11 License generation)\n- testSingleLinkTemplateId (from Phase 9 SingleLink creation)\n- testUserId (from user creation operations)\n\nIf IDs are not captured, these tests will gracefully handle 404 responses.",
